LCAS System Architecture and Technical Diagrams

Figure 1: Lunar Cognitive Autonomy Stack (LCAS) - Complete System Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                           STRATEGIC LOOP (Asynchronous)                      │
│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │
│  │                    Layer 5: Cooperative Intelligence                  │   │
